{"tid":281759,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"【E32017】史上最強家用機Xbox One X　11月7日推出","createTime":"2017-06-13T01:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-13T02:30:10.000Z","uid":28366,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75293e5f93576d440a79a9ba640b377d1eb5c348","tid":281759,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170613/large/vsub80504.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170613%2Flarge%2Fvsub80504.png&h=d46f3494&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMicrosoft終於都在E3展前發佈會上公開代號為「Project Scorpio」新遊戲主機的面紗，正式名稱亦非之前流出的Xbox10 S，而是Xbox One X，主打4K遊戲。Xbox One X硬件規格無可置疑地強，由處理器到圖像處理器的運動能力都較同級對手PS4 Pro為高，而且最難得是內置4K UHD Blu-ray光碟機的Xbox One X一改以往「肥大肉厚」的機身設計，新機除了比PS4 Pro細，甚至Microsoft亦形容為史上最細的Xbox主機，相信部份原因都歸功於新加入的水冷系統，即使只採用較細機箱都能保持良好的散熱效果。 <br />\n<br />\n新機定於11月7日陸續在世界各地推出，香港幾時推出就未見公佈，屆時除了可玩到4K製作的新Xbox One遊戲如《Forza Motorsport7》等之外，不少之前已推出的遊戲如《Gears of War4》、《Minecraft》、《Killer Instinct》、《Forza Horizon3》、《Halo Wars2》、《Final Fantasy15》及《Resident Evil7》等，都可經由下載更新檔支援到4K輸出。不過講到價錢就是另一個問題，Xbox One X開價499美元（約$3,890），是目前定價最高的遊戲主機，比同級對手PS4 Pro貴了足足100美元（約$780）。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170613/large/vsub80505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170613%2Flarge%2Fvsub80505.jpg&h=65583c14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20170613/large/vsub80506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20170613%2Flarge%2Fvsub80506.jpg&h=ebd73bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nXbox One X<br />\n推出日期：2017年11月7日開始<br />\n售價：499美元（約$3,890）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170613/20053834\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170613%2F20053834&d=Zw7RsjXkRf0%2FmFxYRgkQuzACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=9b4310ed\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fsupplement%2Ftech%2Fart%2F20170613%2F20053834&h=c3073c6a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/tech/art/20170613/20053834</a>"},{"pid":"6f5120afd3050bdb276946a73e4200f0c13aee95","tid":281759,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:45:25.000Z","msg":"等Xbox Two"},{"pid":"17332d7f1bf0592a8a9ee0998f34dddd4b55bd7c","tid":281759,"uid":35589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T01:59:42.000Z","msg":"又要貴過PS4又要廢過PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af18b11653118b71f04a1d77ff64653b77bc9429","tid":281759,"uid":4200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要貴過PS4又要廢過PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n硬件廢過PS4??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e896c1835bd9ab1abfb6e6bc4e1dacb35d2370e3","tid":281759,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:04:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又要貴過PS4又要廢過PS4<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df5846617c4e4aed8780dc2aa2b3bf9aba7efca8","tid":281759,"uid":72422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-13T02:30:10.000Z","msg":"必買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj